パッケージの使用
org.interledger.codecs

  • org.interledger.codecsを使用しているパッケージ 
    パッケージ 説明
    org.interledger.codecs
    This package holds all codecs for the Interledger project, including top-level interfaces and abstract classes that can be utilized to create more specific codecs, such as for ASN.1 OER, JSON, Protobuf, and more.
    org.interledger.codecs.oer  
    org.interledger.codecs.oer.ilp  
    org.interledger.codecs.oer.ilqp  
    org.interledger.codecs.oer.ipr  
    org.interledger.codecs.psk  
  • org.interledger.codecsにより使用されるorg.interledger.codecsのクラス 
    クラスと説明
    Codec
    A generic coder/decoder interface for all Interledger objects.
    CodecContext
    A contextual object for matching instances of Codec to specific class types.
    InterledgerPacketCodec
    An implementation of Codec that reads and writes instances of InterledgerPacket having a discrete InterledgerPacketType and data payload.
